By far my favorite way to make money in 2023. Sports betting and fantasy sports are blowing up. There are new apps popping up everyday and the way they get new users is they raise money from venture capitalists then pay that money to influencers to bring in new users. I’ve helped dozens of people make a living doing this and it’s super fun if you are a sports fan.

I wasted so much time going to college. I was programmed to trust my parents and seek their approval, but my parents never lived the life I want my family to live. Growing up we always had to be aware of how we spent our money because we had to live on a budget. Once I dropped out I learned skills that have allowed me to make as high as $180,000 in one month and now my wife and I really never worry about how much anything costs. If we need something done we pay someone else to do it for us and this allows us to have a ton of time to do the things we actually want to.

This is a super realistic way to start a side hustle outside of your 9-5 that can eventually replace your 9-5. The hardest time is when you have to balance both but once you quit your job and can fully focus on resell you’ll quickly get to where you can make 50-100k/yr working 15hr weeks. For me this allowed me to spend 40hrs each week learning things that I would eventually use to achieve my first six figure months. Becoming an Amazon seller and mastering retail arbitrage is such a great thing to get good at. For many people that’s where they stop. They’re making 100-200k a year working 30hr weeks and that gives them all they want out of life.

Door to door sales changed my life. The skills I learned gave me a ton of confidence. Then just seeing so many goofy ass dudes make 250k+ changed my personal expectations for myself. I used to think that if I made 100k a year I’d be happy. Once I saw so many people that I knew I was better than make 100-250k I changed my mindset to 1mil/yr. Now my goal is a million dollar month. Surrounding yourself with savages will always help you level up!

This technique is called SMMA which stands for social media marketing agency. Right now most business owners are older and didn’t grow up on social media. If you can help these business owners grow on social media they will gladly pay you a full time salary. The best part is once you prove you can help one business, you can then leverage that success story to land 5-10 more businesses in your area.

Retail arbitrage directly at adidas outlets also works well too. I like buying adidas from their stores because they have awesome discounts plus if you get the adidas app you can earn 30% off coupons that make your profit margins even more insane.
